  "description": {
    "zh": "嗯你好，好久不见。我知道最近对你和我来说都是困难时期，但这对我们俩来说都可能是美好的一天——如果你决定帮助我的话！\n\n现在让我们谈正事，当地人拦截了最近一直在流通的武器运输，这里没什么不寻常的，但这里的问题是接收这些武器的人，他们除了麻烦什么也没造成！他们甚至比当地人渣更糟糕，我们必须从根源上处理这个问题。\n\n所以我再次请你帮个忙，我不能允许这些武器在塔科夫流通，来吧，你知道如果你在这里搭把手对每个人都更好。",
    "en": "Well hello, long time no see. I know times were difficult for you and me recently, but this can be a good day for both of us - If you decide to help me of course!\n\nNow let's talk business, locals have intercepted weapon shipments that have been going around recently, nothing unusual here, but the problem here is the people that receive these weapons, they are causing nothing but trouble! They are even worse than the local scum, and we have to treat this by it's roots.\n\nSo I am asking you for a favor again, I can't allow these weapons to circulate around Tarkov, come on you know it's better for everyone if you lend a hand here."
  },
